Guthan's helm from Last Man Standing is a minigame-exclusive variant of the normal Guthan's helm. It can be obtained from opening the chests with a bloody key or bloodier key, or looting the crates that spawn at random locations on the map. It can be looted from other players as it always drops on death. It is only available inside the minigame and does not degrade.

For more details on the mechanics and strategies for this equipment, see the set page.
